    "%@, %@": {
      "comment": "A label that combines the title of the capsule with a subtitle describing its current state. The first argument is the title of the capsule. The second argument is the string “Готова открыться”, the string “%1$arg · открыта %2$arg”, or the string “Открытие: %@”.",
